overview: ROH Winter Warriors Tour 2015 Night 1 was a professional wrestling event produced by Ring of Honor (ROH). It took place on January 30, 2015 at the Ford Community & Performing Arts Center in Dearborn, Michigan. It featured a main event of ROH World Champion Jay Lethal defending his title against challenger and former champ, Roderick Strong.
title: ROH: Winter Warriors Tour - Dearborn
